replies.body:
> Also, when you say "Killer", do you mean it's too high or too low? 

It's kind of high, I mean I understand that it gives a sizable buff to the team. I would stay within the range of 160/140/120 as a cool down duration. As for the scaling of the attack damage, I'd say something like 48 (+2.3 per level) { 2.3 x 18 + 48}. Most of his kit is magic damage or health based so there's not that much of a need for high AD scaling. And the health regen could be buffed, lower the base health regen to 7.5 with ( + .87 per level) {.87 x 18 + 7.5} that way that he doesn't fall off later in the game. Glad to help :) 

{{champion:33}}
